data.description: Discover the appeal and character of this newly listed gem in Hampton. This residence stands proudly on a spacious corner lot, offering both privacy and a sense of openness. The exterior features a covert patio providing the perfect setting for outdoors gatherings of quite moments of relaxation. Step inside to find a tasteful blend of contemporary design with farmhouse charm. The 2000+sqft boast a family room, kitchen with eat in area and 4 bedrooms with a separate office that could be a 5th bedroom. Recent upgrades included a newer roof, ceramic tile throughout the main level,  Stylish kitchen remodel featuring stainless steel appliances and custom wood details in the 1st floor primary bedroom. This conveniently located colonial is ready for you to call home.
